4
00:01:25,922 --> 00:01:26,922
The fortune-teller's words

5
00:01:26,922 --> 00:01:28,762
have aroused Master Jizhou's suspicions.

6
00:01:30,482 --> 00:01:31,281
Mother, calm down.

7
00:01:34,241 --> 00:01:35,762
You are meticulous and astute.

8
