(Master instructed you)

9
00:01:38,721 --> 00:01:40,042
to prepare a clean set of tea utensils.

10
00:01:40,322 --> 00:01:41,682
Just use plain water, not tea.

11
00:01:41,922 --> 00:01:42,721
Do it carefully.

12
00:01:42,881 --> 00:01:43,762
Don't make a mistake.

13
00:01:48,042 --> 00:01:49,602
I'll take care of it.
You do your things.

14
00:01:50,242 --> 00:01:52,194
(Alum, Star Anise, Salt)

15
00:01:52,602 --> 00:01:54,562
(To think of adding alum to the water)

16
00:01:54,842 --> 00:01:55,842
(to help the blood)

17
00:01:55,842 --> 00:01:57,202
(of Jizhou and Shuangshuang merge.)

18
00:01:57,881 --> 00:02:00,482
Just a petty trick to muddle through.

19
00:02:01,322 --> 00:02:02,682
But, after that,

20
00:02:02,922 --> 00:02:04,602
I guess Uncle will no longer

21
00:02:04,602 --> 00:02:06,042
have any doubts about it.

22
00:02:06,441 --> 00:02:07,081
Mmm.

23
00:02:09,521 --> 00:02:12,202
One more thing.

24
00:02:12,801 --> 00:02:15,361
Since Uncle will no longer
doubt Shuangshuang's origins,

25
00:02:15,681 --> 00:02:18,081
there's no point in keeping Ms. Li.

26
00:02:18,722 --> 00:02:19,762
How should she be dealt with?

27
00:02:20,482 --> 00:02:21,801
You mean...

28
00:02:29,961 --> 00:02:30,681
Miss.

29
00:02:31,121 --> 00:02:32,482
Early this morning, I inquired

30
00:02:32,482 --> 00:02:34,442
of the servants
I got along with in the Luo's.

31
00:02:34,762 --> 00:02:37,202
But they told me nothing had happened.

32
00:02:37,561 --> 00:02:38,681
Nothing happened?

33
00:02:40,882 --> 00:02:42,081
But Luo Jizhou

34
00:02:42,081 --> 00:02:43,841
doesn't seem like someone
who can keep his cool.

35
00:02:44,202 --> 00:02:45,561
He's bound to do something.

36
00:02:46,922 --> 00:02:49,162
He would surely take
Luo Shuangshuang to verify it.

37
00:02:49,641 --> 00:02:52,121
And the most direct way
is through a paternity test using blood.

38
00:02:52,722 --> 00:02:55,042
If he finds out Luo Shuangshuang
is not his biological daughter,

39
00:02:55,282 --> 00:02:57,722
he'd turn their mansion upside down.

40
00:02:58,841 --> 00:03:00,681
But nothing has happened?

41
00:03:02,322 --> 00:03:04,681
Could it be that someone else
in the mansion has interfered?

42
00:03:07,681 --> 00:03:09,681
If the truth isn't verified,

43
00:03:11,162 --> 00:03:12,521
Luo Jizhou

44
00:03:13,561 --> 00:03:14,521
will only be more convinced

45
00:03:14,521 --> 00:03:16,882
Luo Shuangshuang
is his biological daughter.

46
00:03:17,722 --> 00:03:19,042
We couldn't find the midwife.

47
00:03:19,442 --> 00:03:20,841
And the fortune-teller failed too.

48
00:03:21,361 --> 00:03:23,322
What should we do?

49
00:03:26,762 --> 00:03:27,521
The midwife.

50
00:03:28,841 --> 00:03:30,002
She is our last hope.

51
00:03:30,641 --> 00:03:32,202
Once she is no longer of use,

52
00:03:32,602 --> 00:03:34,042
the Luo family will get rid of her.

53
00:03:34,361 --> 00:03:36,282
So we just need
to follow their men closely.

54
00:03:36,841 --> 00:03:38,322
Then we will be able to find

55
00:03:39,361 --> 00:03:40,482
Ms. Li.

56
00:03:43,801 --> 00:03:44,482
Enjoy.

57
00:03:47,442 --> 00:03:50,922
General Xu, are you going
to join me for the farewell meal?

58
00:03:55,121 --> 00:03:56,681
You're overthinking it.

59
00:03:57,322 --> 00:03:58,961
This is just a normal meal.

60
00:03:59,602 --> 00:04:00,801
As a woman,

61
00:04:01,282 --> 00:04:03,282
you've made your way
to the leader of the black market,

62
00:04:03,722 --> 00:04:04,922
known as Know-it-all.

63
00:04:05,602 --> 00:04:07,521
Honestly, I admire you.

64
00:04:08,202 --> 00:04:10,442
This is the cargo box
from Shen Escort Agency.

65
00:04:10,801 --> 00:04:13,282
The lock hole here has been corroded
by the Dissolving Powder.

66
00:04:14,081 --> 00:04:16,602
The item inside was stolen by someone
with exceptional lightness skills

67
00:04:17,201 --> 00:04:20,282
who's also a master of poison.

68
00:04:20,522 --> 00:04:21,962
So I'd like to inquire

69
00:04:22,241 --> 00:04:23,602
about who this person really is.

70
00:04:27,042 --> 00:04:27,561
