71
00:04:28,201 --> 00:04:29,121
The general is asking you.

72
00:04:29,121 --> 00:04:29,801
Tianhao.

73
00:04:34,801 --> 00:04:35,761
You don't have to tell me

74
00:04:36,282 --> 00:04:37,121
if you don't want to.

75
00:04:37,962 --> 00:04:40,561
After the meal,
Tianhao will escort you back.

76
00:04:41,321 --> 00:04:41,842
I'm leaving.

77
00:04:46,282 --> 00:04:46,984
Oh, right.

78
00:04:47,602 --> 00:04:49,321
I sent the beggars
to a charity organization

79
00:04:49,842 --> 00:04:50,801
offering food and shelter.

80
00:04:51,441 --> 00:04:53,321
Later, they can also attend
a free school to study.

81
00:04:55,441 --> 00:04:56,282
General Xu.

82
00:04:56,761 --> 00:04:57,321
Thank you.

83
00:05:00,361 --> 00:05:01,082
General Xu,

84
00:05:01,482 --> 00:05:03,602
the first rule of the black market is

85
00:05:03,602 --> 00:05:05,761
not to do business with the officials.

86
00:05:06,321 --> 00:05:08,121
I must abide by it.

87
00:05:10,922 --> 00:05:11,441
Okay.

88
00:05:11,761 --> 00:05:13,162
I'll ask an unrelated question.

89
00:05:13,922 --> 00:05:15,522
The girl I saved that day.

90
00:05:16,162 --> 00:05:17,441
What did she come to you for?

91
00:05:19,042 --> 00:05:22,121
She wanted me to find
a midwife surnamed Li.

92
00:05:22,922 --> 00:05:24,001
A midwife surnamed Li.

93
00:05:28,162 --> 00:05:29,282
Go back to have your meal.

94
00:05:34,082 --> 00:05:34,801
General,

95
00:05:35,241 --> 00:05:36,922
why are you asking
about Miss Shen again?

96
00:05:38,922 --> 00:05:40,922
The esteemed young lady
of Shen Escort Agency

97
00:05:41,241 --> 00:05:42,842
seeks information from the black market.

98
00:05:44,282 --> 00:05:45,602
She is

99
00:05:45,801 --> 00:05:47,162
really full of surprises.

100
00:05:48,001 --> 00:05:49,962
I'm going to conduct
a thorough investigation.

101
00:05:55,761 --> 00:05:57,681
He just sent her
the wound-healing cream to make nice.

102
00:05:58,321 --> 00:06:00,162
And he's planning to investigate
Miss Shen again?

103
00:06:00,922 --> 00:06:02,321
Wouldn't it be counterproductive?

104
00:06:13,042 --> 00:06:14,441
So she's hidden in another mansion.

105
00:06:15,001 --> 00:06:15,962
Act according to the plan.

106
00:06:16,162 --> 00:06:17,441
Before the Luo family takes action,

107
00:06:17,642 --> 00:06:18,962
we need to find Ms. Li.

108
00:06:19,162 --> 00:06:19,681
Mmm.

109
00:06:25,201 --> 00:06:26,042
What are you looking at?

110
00:06:28,361 --> 00:06:29,482
Why is it you again?

111
00:06:30,602 --> 00:06:32,842
I saw you having a conflict
with the beggars at the black market.

112
00:06:33,082 --> 00:06:34,881
I thought you got involved
in some dangerous affair.

113
00:06:35,241 --> 00:06:35,922
However,

114
00:06:36,361 --> 00:06:38,001
you've come to eavesdrop
outside Luo's mansion.

115
00:06:38,522 --> 00:06:39,602
Don't you have

116
00:06:39,722 --> 00:06:41,082
anything better to do?

117
00:06:41,881 --> 00:06:43,001
I'm working on official business,

118
00:06:43,321 --> 00:06:44,482
and I just happened to come by.

119
00:06:44,962 --> 00:06:46,801
Hurry on with your thing.

120
00:06:46,801 --> 00:06:47,761
I've got some to do too.

121
00:06:48,121 --> 00:06:50,082
I don't have the time to chat with you.

122
00:06:50,482 --> 00:06:51,042
Well,

123
00:06:51,321 --> 00:06:52,361
what I'm gonna take care of

124
00:06:52,642 --> 00:06:53,441
is you.

125
00:06:54,321 --> 00:06:55,121
Miss.

126
00:06:55,121 --> 00:06:56,761
The general is gonna take care of you.

127
00:07:01,241 --> 00:07:03,121
Shuixian, you make it sound strange.

128
00:07:05,321 --> 00:07:07,042
I'm here to save someone.
There's no time to waste.

129
00:07:07,482 --> 00:07:08,561
The Luos want to kill Ms. Li.

130
00:07:08,962 --> 00:07:10,922
I'm afraid they might be
making a move inside right now.

131
00:07:11,241 --> 00:07:13,441
Murder cases happen
to be my responsibility.

132
00:07:14,681 --> 00:07:15,441
What are you doing?

133
00:07:16,042 --> 00:07:16,602
Don't shout.

134
00:07:17,922 --> 00:07:18,522
Let go of me.

135
00:07:18,602 --> 00:07:19,201
How dare you!

136
00:07:19,441 --> 00:07:21,561
General Xu is here. What are you doing?

137
00:07:22,761 --> 00:07:23,336
Run!

138
00:07:23,801 --> 00:07:24,602
I was freaked out.

139
00:07:25,162 --> 00:07:25,768
Heavens.

140
00:07:25,881 --> 00:07:26,561
Ms. Li.

141
00:07:27,001 --> 00:07:28,121
- The Luos want you dead.
- Lady.

142
00:07:28,121 --> 00:07:29,962
If it weren't for us,
you'd be dead by now.

143
00:07:30,082 --> 00:07:31,962
I don't need to spell it out, do I?

144
00:07:32,441 --> 00:07:33,962
I'm not very smart,

145
00:07:34,121 --> 00:07:35,922
but I can tell who means well to me

146
00:07:35,922 --> 00:07:36,761
and who wants to harm me.

147
00:07:37,201 --> 00:07:39,241
Thank you for saving my life. Thank you.

148
00:07:39,241 --> 00:07:41,361
Tianhao, take Ms. Li back.

149
00:07:41,681 --> 00:07:42,201
Yes.

150
00:07:43,441 --> 00:07:43,962
Okay.

151
00:07:43,962 --> 00:07:44,681
Miss.

152
00:07:50,522 --> 00:07:51,042
Thank you.

153
00:07:51,842 --> 00:07:52,441
You're welcome.

154
00:07:52,801 --> 00:07:53,761
Just taking a break.

155
00:07:55,801 --> 00:07:56,482
Please.

156
00:08:00,162 --> 00:08:01,361
(Zuiyun Tower)
Take care.

157
00:08:02,441 --> 00:08:03,482
Take care.

158
00:08:11,801 --> 00:08:13,162
Your invitation

159
00:08:14,162 --> 00:08:15,681
wouldn't be a setup, would it?

160
00:08:17,042 --> 00:08:17,642
Master Jizhou,

161
00:08:17,761 --> 00:08:18,602
please, have a seat.

162
00:08:23,042 --> 00:08:23,602
Go ahead.

163
00:08:24,441 --> 00:08:25,082
What's the matter?

164
00:08:25,962 --> 00:08:26,602
Master Jizhou,

165
00:08:26,962 --> 00:08:28,042
take it easy.

166
00:08:28,321 --> 00:08:29,241
Just two people

167
00:08:29,642 --> 00:08:31,121
want to see you.

168
00:08:31,321 --> 00:08:32,882
They want to tell you something.

169
00:08:35,201 --> 00:08:36,122
Come in.

170
00:08:42,601 --> 00:08:43,522
Ms. Li?

171
00:08:44,081 --> 00:08:45,201
Master Jizhou,

172
00:08:45,561 --> 00:08:47,441
help me.

173
00:08:47,642 --> 00:08:48,642
What do you mean by that?

174
00:08:49,002 --> 00:08:51,642
Actually, Miss Shuangshuang
was not a full-term baby.

175
00:08:51,642 --> 00:08:53,441
She was a preterm baby
born in the seventh month.

176
00:08:53,642 --> 00:08:55,481
Madam instructed me to tell you

177
00:08:55,481 --> 00:08:57,841
that Miss Shuangshuang
was born at full term.

178
00:08:58,321 --> 00:09:00,681
She also promised to repay
my gambling debts for me.

179
00:09:00,681 --> 00:09:02,801
So I believed her and deceived you.

180
00:09:03,201 --> 00:09:05,042
But she went back on her word.

181
00:09:05,201 --> 00:09:06,801
She even sent someone
to the mansion I was in

182
00:09:07,042 --> 00:09:09,002
to kill me!

183
00:09:09,721 --> 00:09:11,081
She wants to kill you?

184
00:09:11,362 --> 00:09:13,282
Master Jizhou, think about it.

185
00:09:13,762 --> 00:09:15,282
It's not a big deal

186
00:09:15,282 --> 00:09:16,762
that Miss Shuangshuang
was born prematurely.

187
00:09:16,762 --> 00:09:19,042
But why would Madam Zhou
even want to kill someone

188
00:09:19,042 --> 00:09:20,042
just to hide it from you?

189
00:09:20,481 --> 00:09:21,882
I have served her for so many years.

190
00:09:22,762 --> 00:09:25,122
She appears to be virtuous and good.

191
00:09:25,441 --> 00:09:28,122
But in reality, she is more resolute
and ruthless than anyone.

192
00:09:28,282 --> 00:09:29,721
As long as it benefits her,

193
00:09:30,002 --> 00:09:31,441
she does anything.

194
00:09:31,961 --> 00:09:32,882
Impossible.

195
00:09:33,922 --> 00:09:35,242
I did a paternity test.

196
00:09:36,762 --> 00:09:38,362
The blood merged.

197
00:09:40,201 --> 00:09:41,762
It merged.

198
00:09:42,282 --> 00:09:44,002
But did you check the water

199
00:09:44,362 --> 00:09:45,362
used for the test?

200
00:09:45,922 --> 00:09:47,122
All the people in the mansion

201
00:09:47,122 --> 00:09:49,081
enticed Ms. Li to deceive you.

202
00:09:49,362 --> 00:09:50,801
Of course, it was easy for them

203
00:09:51,081 --> 00:09:52,882
to swap the water used
for the paternity test.

204
00:09:54,681 --> 00:09:55,441
Impossible.

205
00:09:56,002 --> 00:09:56,801
Impossible.

206
00:09:56,801 --> 00:09:57,441
People

207
00:09:57,561 --> 00:09:59,002
are always afraid to face the truth.

208
00:09:59,882 --> 00:10:02,762
Especially those who are
inherently timid.

209
00:10:04,681 --> 00:10:05,481
Master Jizhou,

210
00:10:05,762 --> 00:10:07,922
don't tell me you'd rather be a coward

211
00:10:08,522 --> 00:10:09,961
even if they make a fool of you.

212
00:10:11,522 --> 00:10:13,321
Actually, it is very simple
to figure it out.

213
00:10:13,882 --> 00:10:15,801
Just redo the test.

214
00:10:16,642 --> 00:10:18,762
That's all I want to say.

215
00:10:19,362 --> 00:10:20,762
It's up to you to decide.

216
00:10:22,721 --> 00:10:23,481
Impossible.

217
00:10:24,201 --> 00:10:25,122
This can't be.

218
00:10:26,601 --> 00:10:27,922
How could this happen?

219
00:10:28,922 --> 00:10:30,002
Impossible.

220
00:10:34,642 --> 00:10:35,922
I told Luo Jizhou

221
00:10:35,922 --> 00:10:37,201
all the truth.

222
00:10:37,801 --> 00:10:39,042
His lifelong hope

223
00:10:39,321 --> 00:10:40,522
is to have kids.

224
00:10:42,321 --> 00:10:43,561
If he finds out that Luo Shuangshuang

225
00:10:43,561 --> 00:10:45,162
is not his biological daughter,

226
00:10:45,162 --> 00:10:46,721
he will not let her and her mother off.

227
00:10:50,561 --> 00:10:51,201
And well,

228
00:10:52,081 --> 00:10:53,922
those two women
are not easy to deal with.

229
00:10:54,841 --> 00:10:56,721
They have become accustomed
to a life of luxury.

230
00:10:57,282 --> 00:10:58,601
How could they give up

231
00:10:58,961 --> 00:11:00,721
the power they already have?

232
00:11:01,561 --> 00:11:02,321
When the time comes,

233
00:11:02,721 --> 00:11:03,922
they will surely turn on each other.

234
00:11:05,441 --> 00:11:06,242
And then,

235
00:11:07,201 --> 00:11:08,721
it will be our time to act.

236
00:11:11,481 --> 00:11:12,762
I know you're strategic.

237
00:11:13,201 --> 00:11:14,481
But there's a great risk involved,

238
00:11:15,441 --> 00:11:16,561
especially considering

239
00:11:16,721 --> 00:11:18,721
you are once again openly
opposing the Luo family,

240
00:11:19,282 --> 00:11:20,922
which will inevitably
arouse their vigilance.

241
00:11:21,362 --> 00:11:22,601
You must be careful.

242
00:11:24,002 --> 00:11:24,642
Mmm.

243
00:11:27,321 --> 00:11:27,882
Zishan,

244
00:11:28,201 --> 00:11:29,922
you should take care of yourself.

245
00:11:30,042 --> 00:11:31,122
You look so pale.

246
00:11:31,681 --> 00:11:32,721
Is something troubling you?

247
00:11:34,801 --> 00:11:35,841
Nothing.

248
00:11:36,642 --> 00:11:37,721
I just didn't sleep well.

249
00:11:43,650 --> 00:11:45,640
(Luo Residence)

250
00:11:47,642 --> 00:11:48,441
Miss Shuangshuang,

251
00:11:48,441 --> 00:11:50,122
Master Jizhou wants you
to go to the Zuiyun Tower.

252
00:11:50,522 --> 00:11:51,762
He only asked me to go?

253
00:11:51,882 --> 00:11:52,520
Yes.

254
00:11:52,642 --> 00:11:54,201
The carriage is waiting outside.

255
00:11:54,321 --> 00:11:55,642
Please go.

256
00:11:56,841 --> 00:11:57,681
Be careful.

257
00:11:59,642 --> 00:12:00,961
There are no more issues, I guess.

258
00:12:01,762 --> 00:12:02,841
Madam, Miss Xue'er.

259
00:12:03,522 --> 00:12:04,601
Who has gone out?

260
00:12:05,002 --> 00:12:07,042
Master Jizhou sent someone over

261
00:12:07,042 --> 00:12:09,561
to take Miss Shuangshuang
to see him in the Zuiyun Tower.

262
00:12:10,721 --> 00:12:12,522
Isn't he supposed

263
00:12:12,522 --> 00:12:13,922
to be talking business
with Shen Danqing?

264
00:12:14,042 --> 00:12:15,002
Does he need Shuangshuang?

265
00:12:16,481 --> 00:12:17,841
Ms. Li disappeared.

266
00:12:18,362 --> 00:12:20,441
Uncle asked Shuangshuang
to see him in the Zuiyun Tower.

267
00:12:21,042 --> 00:12:23,002
Something's not right.
Prepare a carriage right away.

268
00:12:23,122 --> 00:12:24,122
We'll go to the Zuiyun Tower.

269
00:12:24,642 --> 00:12:25,224
Alright.

270
00:12:27,841 --> 00:12:28,456
Father.

271
